nly BR fulfills the requirement. The\nBR metric plays an important role in the exploration of new principles in\nfundamental physical theories; we briefly mention some examples related to the\nhorizon of a black hole and the dilaton in string theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2005 13:20:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
